Step 1: Find suitaible branch for your ros version (for most of the cases master branch is okay)

step 2: In the scr of catkin_ws of ros clone the source using the following command
git clone -b <branch-name(like noetic-devel)> <git-site(like //github.com/....)>

step 3: cd ~/catkin_ws

step 4: catkin_make

step 5: source it 

source ~/catkin_ws/devel/setup.bash

step 6: ensure that you do not need to do it again and again:

echo "source ~/catkin_ws/devel/setup.bash" >> ~/.bashrc
